Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:50.69,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\c&H20ECFF&\3c&H050506&\frz355.876\pos(594,194)}CHILIPOT汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:50.69,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}{\c&HF1F1F9&\3c&H8B5D41&}CHILI POT是辣椒锅，也有发型中的锅盖头的意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先去看看再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 今天船长不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 是还没有来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先看看鱼竿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼竿的话 我推荐这一边的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有喷漆镀膜 非常轻便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫做「unsanding」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.79,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF1F1F9&\3c&H5A3F2E&\fs35}unsanding，sanding是磨毛的意思，这里就是不磨毛。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这根啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LUNAMIS S900ML
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于初学者来说 是个不错的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「LUNAMIS」啊 可以说是为钓海鲈而量身定做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,价格适中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个钓竿的厉害之处在于
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上拥有顶级的S系列所有的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}试着挥挥看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 握着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样子把鱼竿的顶端向下压
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能看出硬度和弯曲度的差别了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的货色才37500日元 我觉得真是捡大便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 要配那根钓竿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推荐这一个线轮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TWIN POWER C3000HG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.35,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F1F9&\3c&H5A3F2E&\fs35\an8}西玛诺纺车轮 大概要2K+
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我选的话还是「stela」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一款呢 性能很好 价钱却相当实惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把「stela」比作是钓鱼爱好者所憧憬的公主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一款就相当于是校园的麦当娜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 高中生的你们也能负担得起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪看上去很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十…十万？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓竿和线轮 还有拟饵和钓线之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂七杂八都加起来的话 差不多这个价
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想要钓鱼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么些钱还是得花的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪来这么多钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热死了热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么热的天 人都快要化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 你的星球也会热吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会哦 超级凉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他认识小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是羡慕嫉妒恨啊 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了吗 海咲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错啊 一定很适合炎炎夏日去度假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 那边的印度人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在店里面你就不能把头上的包布摘掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是看看就热
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 少年 你也钓鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海咲 老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 滚烫的红茶 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是船长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是我的大哥一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 小步是个超好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当店员不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼总可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？钓鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树 钓鱼也没法挣钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有能挣钱的路子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能让我们三人来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个想在你的钓鱼船上打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在钓鱼船上打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面试？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得面带笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船长 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙对钓鱼不是半吊子的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何也想要有自己的渔具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 合格！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶 合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天开始就过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多关照~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要上了我的船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天就让你成为海上男儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海上男儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是小步 真是可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 失陪下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}恋爱女神降临了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太棒了 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}女神 我爱你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过劳动来赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过光凭这些就能提高钓鱼技术了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是在船上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都可以钓个尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪要是真就这样提高钓术的话也没什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小岛 盖饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  可可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好有点渴 这次就饶了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能太过去那边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在的话就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是指的谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来目的不只是钓鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.81,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H313168&\fs70\pos(292,191)}极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.81,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H313168&\fs70\pos(995,205)}密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.81,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(647,700)\c&H4A7890&}duck本部长最重要案件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(486,145)\fs35}duck最重要案件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(766,231)\fs35}百慕大综合征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(415,328)\fs35}主要现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(647,446)\fs35}船舶消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(648,523)\fs35}船舱消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(885,590)\fs35}船员短期失忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百慕大综合征就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛罗里达半岛前端的波多黎各岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和百慕大列岛组成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}被称之为百慕大三角的三角形海域内发生的异常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}船只和飞机消失的无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}另外指南针和机器也会出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:32.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,没办法了 我也必须一起去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,不 这只是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这晴朗的夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是鲯鳅之日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.13,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30\c&HF1F1F9&\3c&H5A3F2E&}鲯鳅：（学名：Coryphaenahippurus），俗名三保公鱼、白虎、海(鱼廉)、鬼头刀、\N舢板跳鱼鲯鳅体延长侧扁，前部高大，向后渐变细。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想钓鲯鳅～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲯鳅个头很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有差不多2米左右的家伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓其实不难钓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们太不老实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拽线的力量很大 很有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表也很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋的时候会变颜色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想钓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙要干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要干嘛？ 钓鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多关照了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 果然是来对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船是会晃成这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 小春 拿抄网
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么夏树不动如山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抄网
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抄网×N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也得去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抄网×N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分满分！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全有问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树好狡猾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在钓了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在做引导
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引导？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲯鳅引导员（instructor）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务就是钓上第一条鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种鱼只要有一条上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的鱼就会跟着来咬钩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人就都能钓到鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树 你这眼镜好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是偏光镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上这个就能看清水里的鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 好棒哦 借我戴×4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下借你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人一钓上鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就马上去抄鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大鱼的话 要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水平的话很容易折断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪也是 拜托咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请下杆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥 帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥 这边也上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来啊
